Class Engine

java.lang.Object
com.javax0.logiqua.engine.Engine
All Implemented Interfaces:
Builder, com.javax0.logiqua.Executor
public class Engine extends Object implements com.javax0.logiqua.Executor, Builder
The Engine class represents a script execution framework that can load, manage, and execute operations (commands and functions). It acts as both an Executor and a Builder.

The Engine loads operations from the service loader mechanism and provides APIs to access and update operations. Additionally, the Engine allows the creation of nodes for operations and supports working with constant values in scripts.
